      "writtenOn": "2018-06-25T23:29:56Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Shouldn\u0027t we check if the same fixed state is enabled on both sides, and then if their fixed values are equal, rather than comparing pointers?",
      "revId": "ccf89f45387c23e8a4689e961a7f3d7b6f5c3c61",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
